{
  "stem": "7358.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh-oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We better stop.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finally the construction of the big log that I told you that we dug it into our mountain, like one way, was completed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we moved in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I mentioned to you that before long, there was a house full of people, that my aunt could not refuse for various reasons.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we lived in that place fairly-- I mean, it was very crowded.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I mean, it was-- we felt safe, because my uncle was there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And his son was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had the weapons.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were fairly secluded into an area away from major, major passageways near a swamp on one hand and a mountain on the other hand.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And food was already-- we, at least we had enough food at that point.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- and we heard news from time to time that the Germans are retreating and, and the Russians are coming.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, and was more frequent activities of the, the Russian partisans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were more visible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we heard the various actions they were taking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So our hopes, our hopes were raised again that perhaps somehow we're going to make it through the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was-- in, in comparison to what I lived through prior to that, living in this house was like being on vacation already, being in a resort place, because there was food.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had a big oven.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We could bake our own bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we had meat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we had-- we ate reasonably well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we had enough food, because we lived in the forest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I would say this was already the better part of, of, of the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in February of 1944, we were liberated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
